body: "GH-608. Disjoint-field concurrent edits (A: title, B: body) always conflict solely on the shared updated_at scalar every pm update rewrites. Most common cooperative case, fails 100%. Distinct from pm-9q2t (count headers) and pm-wc1r (history chain). Fix direction: deterministic updated_at resolution (max-wins merge driver) or serialization that isolates volatile scalars from semantic fields."
